### RedEye AI Engine REST API Collection
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client extension
@base_url = http://localhost:8080
@auth_url = http://localhost:8081
@tracer_url = http://localhost:8082
@compliance_url = http://localhost:8083
@cache_url = http://localhost:8084
@api_key = your_virtual_redeye_key
@jwt_token = your_jwt_access_token
@tenant_id = your_tenant_uuid

### ==========================================
### GATEWAY (Client facing)
### ==========================================

### Health Check
GET {{base_url}}/health

### Chat Completions Proxy
POST {{base_url}}/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}
x-tenant-id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai:gpt-4",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Hello, how are you today?" }
  ]
}

### Admin - Metrics
GET {{base_url}}/v1/admin/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Admin - Usage
GET {{base_url}}/v1/admin/metrics/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Admin - Traces
GET {{base_url}}/v1/admin/traces
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Admin - Billing
GET {{base_url}}/v1/admin/billing/breakdown
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}


### ==========================================
### AUTH SERVICE
### ==========================================

### Signup
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@redeye.ai",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "company_name": "RedEye Labs"
}

### Login
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@redeye.ai",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Refresh Token (Relies on cookies)
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/refresh

### Onboard Tenant Strategy
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/onboard
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account_type": "individual",
  "provider": "openai",
  "api_key": "sk-your-openai-key-here",
  "workspace_name": "Personal"
}

### List API Keys
GET {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Request OTP
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/request-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@redeye.ai"
}

### Verify OTP
POST {{auth_url}}/v1/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@redeye.ai",
  "otp_code": "123456"
}


### ==========================================
### COMPLIANCE SERVICE
### ==========================================

### Redact Prompt manually
POST {{compliance_url}}/v1/compliance/redact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Call me at 917-555-0123"
}

### ==========================================
### TRACER SERVICE
### ==========================================

### Ingest Trace manually
POST {{tracer_url}}/v1/traces/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trace_id": "test-trace-abc",
  "session_id": "test-sess",
  "tenant_id": "{{tenant_id}}",
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "status": 200,
  "latency_ms": 250,
  "total_tokens": 12,
  "cache_hit": false,
  "prompt_content": "ping",
  "response_content": "pong"
}

### Get Audit Logs
GET {{tracer_url}}/v1/audit?tenant_id={{tenant_id}}&limit=10

### ==========================================
### CACHE SERVICE
### ==========================================

### Rest Cache Lookup
POST {{cache_url}}/v1/cache/lookup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant_id": "{{tenant_id}}",
  "model": "gpt-4",
  "prompt": "Will it rain tomorrow?"
}
